      <title>北京呼吁韩国奉行“积极、客观、友好”的对华政策</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-calls-positive-objective-friendly-china-policy-south-korea-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外交部长王毅周二在与韩国外长通电话时表示，中国希望韩国奉行“积极、客观、友好”的对华政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-calls-positive-objective-friendly-china-policy-south-korea-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:54:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚国民银行任命安德鲁·欧文为新任首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/national-australia-bank-names-andrew-irvine-new-ceo-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚国民银行周三表示，担任四年多首席执行官的罗斯·麦克尤恩 (Ross McEwan) 将离开该银行，由目前负责业务和私人银行业务的安德鲁·欧文 (Andrew Irvine) 接任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/national-australia-bank-names-andrew-irvine-new-ceo-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 23:44:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国安全委员会关于波音 MAX 9 门板报告的五个事实</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/five-facts-us-safety-board-report-boeing-max-9-door-panel-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国家运输安全委员会周二发布的初步报告显示，1 月 5 日，一架波音 737 MAX 9 喷气式飞机在飞行途中坠毁，门板似乎缺少四个关键螺栓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/five-facts-us-safety-board-report-boeing-max-9-door-panel-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 22:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡星展银行维持 2024 年指引不变，第四季度利润超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/singapore-bank-dbs-fourth-quarter-net-profit-rises-2-on-year-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡最大银行星展集团在第四季度净利润增长 2%，超出预期后，将 2024 年净利息收入指引维持在去年水平左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/singapore-bank-dbs-fourth-quarter-net-profit-rises-2-on-year-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 22:40:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新西兰劳动力压力略有缓解，就业市场依然紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/new-zealands-jobless-rate-rises-40-fourth-quarter-2024-02-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰统计局周三公布的数据显示，新西兰劳动力压力略有缓解，但尽管整体经济有所降温，但该国就业市场仍然紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/new-zealands-jobless-rate-rises-40-fourth-quarter-2024-02-06/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Feb 2024 22:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
